<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB04828</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT TO PROVIDE A SEPARATE BUDGET-SUBSIDY TO THE LOCALIZED COMMUNITY MORTGAGE PROGRAM (LCMP), TO EMPOWER LOCAL GOVERNMENT HOUSING PROGRAMS, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to ensure that the community association (CAs) complies to the submission of requirements, eliminate disputes among members of the CAs, provide sufficient Social Housing Finance Corporation (SHFC) human resource complement for the program and, provide the proper financial assistance.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ROMERO, MICHAEL ODYLON L., Ph.D., PINEDA, ENRICO A.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2017-01-25</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON HOUSING AND URBAN DEVELOPMENT ON 2017-02-01</td></tr></table>